snippet.description:
Get ready to embark on this emotional rollercoaster of the most amazing journey ever taken, as we present to you the Dunki Drop 1.

Starring Shah Rukh Khan, Taapsee Pannu, Boman Irani and Vicky Kaushal, Dunki, directed by Rajkumar Hirani, and presented by Jio Studios, Red Chillies Entertainment and Rajkumar Hirani Films.
#DunkiDrop1

Celebrate Christmas 2023 with your entire family with #Dunki, a heartwarming story of a soldierâ€™s journey to keep a promise!

Ingredients:
Bhajani
â€¢ 2 1/2 cup / 500 gm Rice
â€¢ 1 cup / 200 gm Chana dal
â€¢ 1/2 cup / 100 gm Moong dal
â€¢ 1/2 cup / 100 gm Urad dal
â€¢ 1/2 cup / 100 gm Poha
â€¢ 20 gm Coriander seeds
â€¢ 20 gm Cumin seeds
Chakali
â€¢ 3 cups Water
â€¢ 1/4 cup Oil
â€¢ 1 tsp Oil
â€¢ 1 tsp Red chili powder
â€¢ Salt to taste
â€¢ 1 tbsp Coriander powder
â€¢ 1 kilo Chakali bhajani
â€¢ 1 tsp Ajwain / Carom seeds
â€¢ 1 tsp white Sesame seeds
â€¢ Oil for frying

Method:
â€¢ Wipe the rice really good with a clean wet cotton cloth. 
â€¢ Wipe chana dal really good with clean wet cotton cloth. 
â€¢ Wipe moong dal really good with a clean wet cotton cloth. 
â€¢ Wipe urad dal really good with a clean wet cotton cloth. 
â€¢ You can wash and dry all these ingredients if you want. 
â€¢ Heat up a pan on medium heat and roast rice really good. 
â€¢ The rice should be roasted well but the color should not change. 
â€¢ When the rice is roasted well take it out into a dish. 
â€¢ In the same pan roast chana dal really good until it begins to get reddish color and take it out into 
  a dish. 
â€¢ In the same pan roast moong dal well until it gets reddish color and take it out into a dish. 
â€¢ In the same pan roast urad dal really good until it gets light golden color and take it out into a 
  dish. 
â€¢ Roast poha really good and transfer them into the dish. 
â€¢ In the same pan roast coriander seeds and cumin seeds together on low heat until nice aroma 
  begins to release from it and transfer it into the dish. 
â€¢ Mix everything well together and let it cool down. 
â€¢ Grind it from the mill. Make sure that it is ground after rice or jawar is ground and not after wheat. 
â€¢ Blend it into flour in mixer and sieve it through flour strainer. 
â€¢ Blend the leftover coarse flour in the strain again in blender and sieve it. Bhajani for chakali is 
  ready.
Chakali
â€¢ Heat up water in a pan and add oil. 
â€¢ Mix well and add red chili powder, salt, coriander powder. 
â€¢ Mix well and when the mixture boils really good, reduce the heat to low. 
â€¢ Add the bhajani flour and turn off the gas. 
â€¢ Add carom seeds, sesame seeds and mix everything well together quickly. 
â€¢ Transfer the ukad into a dish and knead dough. If needed use very little hot water. 
â€¢ Knead the ukad really good when it is still hot. The consistency of the dough should be stiff. 
â€¢ Take small portion from the dough and knead it really good again. 
â€¢ Make a smooth and even roll and transfer it into chakali machine. 
â€¢ Press the dough well and roll out chakali from it on a butter paper. 
â€¢ Seal both the ends of the chakali really good. 
â€¢You can use plastic sheet or dish in place of butter paper. 
â€¢ Heat up oil in a pan on medium to high heat for about 6-7 minutes and drop a small chakali in it. 
â€¢ If it is fried well, then the oil is hot enough. 
â€¢ Drop chakali into hot oil and fry well. 
â€¢ When the chakali begins to settle at the bottom, flip it over and fry well from other side too. 
â€¢ When chakali begins to settle at the bottom of the pan, it means it is fried well from both sides. 
â€¢ Take the chakali out, drain excess oil and transfer it into a dish. Chakali is ready.

Todayâ€™s recipe is Diwali faral shankarpali using 1 kilo maida. It turns out nice, crispy and flaky. Diwali faral is incomplete without shankarpali. We already have seen different recipes if shankarpali. This is full proof recipe the proportion used is just perfect. It is a very easy and simple recipe. You can make it within no time. Besides, I am sharing few tips to make perfect shankarpali. This is a popular Marathi recipe. Also it can be a good tea time snack. You can try this recipe at home and drop a comment for me. Do not forget to like, share and subscribe.

Ingredients:
â€¢ 1 cup Milk
â€¢ 1 cup Sugar
â€¢ 1 cup Ghee
â€¢ 7 cups / 1 kilo Maida
â€¢ Oil for frying

Method:
â€¢ Heat up a pan on medium heat and add milk and sugar. 
â€¢ Heat it up together until sugar is dissolved. 
â€¢ When sugar is dissolved and the mixture begins to boil, turn off the gas and add ghee. 
â€¢ Melt ghee before measuring. Make sure you donâ€™t use thick ghee. 
â€¢ Mix well and base for shankarpali is ready. 
â€¢ Transfer the base into the maida and mix in with the help of ladle. 
â€¢ Knead the mixture into dough. 
â€¢ Make small portions of the dough. Keep the leftover dough covered with a wet cloth.
â€¢ Take one portion and roll it into a thick chapati. The thickness of the chapati should be about 1 
  cm. 
â€¢ Cut off the edges and roll the chapati little more if you want. 
â€¢ Cut shankarpali into size and shape you want and take them out into a dish. 
â€¢ Rolled out shankarpali should not dry out. 
â€¢ Heat up oil on high heat for about 5 minutes and reduce the heat to low. 
â€¢ Drop shankarpali into hot oil and fry it well for at least 3-4 minutes. 
â€¢ If oil is hot enough and still shankarpali dissolves in oil, then add a little more maida into the 
  dough. Add a little milk and knead the dough again. Roll out shankarpali and fry. It wonâ€™t dissolve. 
â€¢ When shankarpali gets nice golden color from all sides, take it out, drain excess oil and transfer it 
  into a dish. Shankarpali is ready.
â€¢ You can store them in an air tight container when they cool down completely. They have shelf life 
  of about 1 month.

snippet.title: Kingdom of the Planet of the Apes | Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Director Wes Ball breathes new life into the global, epic franchise set several generations in the future following Caesarâ€™s reign, in which apes are the dominant species living harmoniously and humans have been reduced to living in the shadows. As a new tyrannical ape leader builds his empire, one young ape undertakes a harrowing journey that will cause him to question all that he has known about the past and to make choices that will define a future for apes and humans alike.

â€œKingdom of the Planet of the Apesâ€ is directed by Wes Ball (the â€œMaze Runnerâ€ trilogy) and stars Owen Teague (â€œITâ€), Freya Allan (â€œThe Witcherâ€), Kevin Durand (Locke & Keyâ€), Peter Macon (â€œShamelessâ€), and William H. Macy (â€œFargoâ€). The screenplay is by Josh Friedman (â€œWar of the Worldsâ€) and Rick Jaffa & Amanda Silver (â€œAvatar: The Way of Waterâ€) and Patrick Aison (â€œPreyâ€), based on characters created by Rick Jaffa & Amanda Silver, and the producers are Wes Ball, Joe Hartwick, Jr. (â€œThe Maze Runnerâ€), Rick Jaffa, Amanda Silver, Jason Reed (â€œMulanâ€), with Peter Chernin (the â€œPlanet of the Apesâ€ trilogy) and Jenno Topping (â€œFord v. Ferrariâ€) serving as executive producers.

snippet.title: The Fall Guy | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
The Stuntman becomes the hero. #TheFallGuyMovie only in theaters March 1.

------

Heâ€™s a stuntman, and like everyone in the stunt community, he gets blown up, shot, crashed, thrown through windows and dropped from the highest of heights, all for our entertainment. And now, fresh off an almost career-ending accident, this working-class hero has to track down a missing movie star, solve a conspiracy and try to win back the love of his life while still doing his day job. What could possibly go right? 

From real life stunt man and director David Leitch, the blockbuster director of Bullet Train, Deadpool 2, Atomic Blonde and Fast & Furious Presents: Hobbs & Shaw and the producer of John Wick, Nobody and Violent Night, comes his most personal film yet. A new hilarious, hard-driving, all-star apex-action thriller and love letter to action movies and the hard-working and under-appreciated crew of people who make them: The Fall Guy. 

OscarÂ® nominee Ryan Gosling (Barbie, La La Land, Drive) stars as Colt Seavers, a battle-scarred stuntman who, having left the business a year earlier to focus on both his physical and mental health, is drafted back into service when the star of a mega-budget studio movieâ€”being directed by his ex, Jody Moreno, played by Golden Globe winner Emily Blunt (Oppenheimer, A Quiet Place films, Sicario)â€”goes missing.

While the filmâ€™s ruthless producer (Emmy winner Hannah Waddingham; Ted Lasso), maneuvers to keep the disappearance of star Tom Ryder (Golden Globe winner Aaron Taylor-Johnson; Bullet Train) a secret from the studio and the media, Colt performs the filmâ€™s most outrageous stunts while trying (with limited success) to charm his way back into Jodyâ€™s good graces. But as the mystery around the missing star deepens, Colt will find himself ensnared in a sinister, criminal plot that will push him to the edge of a fall more dangerous than any stunt.

Inspired by the hit 1980s TV series, The Fall Guy also stars Winston Duke (Black Panther franchise) and Academy AwardÂ® nominee Stephanie Hsu (Everything Everywhere All at Once). 

From a screenplay by Hobbs & Shaw screenwriter Drew Pearce, The Fall Guy is produced by Kelly McCormick (Bullet Train, Nobody, Atomic Blonde) and David Leitch for their company 87North, and by Ryan Gosling and by Guymon Casady (Game of Thrones, Steve Jobs and executive producer of the upcoming series Ripley) for Entertainment 360. The film is executive produced by Drew Pearce, Entertainment 360â€™s Geoff Shaevitz and the creator of the original Fall Guy television series, Glen A. Larson.

snippet.title: Milk Sweet recipe in Tamil | Kalakand Recipe in Tamil
snippet.description:
In this video we will see how to make milk sweet recipe in tamil. This milk sweet / Kalakand is made by curdling milk with some lemon juice which creates some precipitated milk curds and these are then caramelized under heat to impart that rich, chewy, caramel taste. Compared to the regular milk sweet, this version has a lot more texture and chewiness to it. This Kalakand recipe is popular during festival time and can be topped with some nuts.
#milksweetrecipe #milksweetrecipeintamil #kalakandrecipe 

Friends, please do try this milk sweet recipe at home and share it with your friends and family. Also, please do share your feedback about the recipe in the comments below. All the best and happy cooking! 

Ingredients:
2 Liter full fat Milk (8 cup)
1 cup Sugar(200g) can be increased to 1.25 cup
juice of half Lemon
2+2 tbsp Ghee
pinch of Cardamom powder

The third film in the universe, "War," was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. The recent release Pathaan (2023) starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham is the fourth instalment in the spy universe franchise.

About me:

The smallest countryside, a beautiful childhood was my past. It is a glorious experience but remains like the memory of a past life.
Due to an endless wish, persistent effort, and a grateful companionship with my better half, I was able to create my little Brindavan in the outskirts of Hyderabad just as I dreamed.
We do not know if it was our mindset, but we managed to create Patnam lo Palleturu- Our little long lost village in the city. 
We believe in living life and not in just Surviving.

I have come forward to have fun with you in a world of small and beautiful dreams.
This includes our home, beautiful garden, our Grandparents' food recipes, health tips, modern steps and the desire to share my thoughts with you.

snippet.title: Leo Post-release Lokesh Kanagaraj Interview with Sudhir Srinivasan | Leo | Vijay | Trisha | Part 1
snippet.description:
In this spoiler-filled interaction with Sudhir Srinivasan, #LokeshKanagaraj talks about all things #Leo, envisioning #Vijay in the LCU, and more 

This is the first part of the interaction.   #CinemaExpress 

00:10 - 01:45  - Loki and The Kerala Story
01:46 - 02:45 - How did Loki respond to the polarising responses 
02:46 - 04:40 - How did Loki accept the criticism about the flashback
04:41 - 08.40 - How Loki fixed the duration of Leo
08:41 - 09:40 - What does Loki believe is the truth of Leo?  
09:41 - 10:54  - What is Loki's favourite thing about the Leo flashback
10:55 - 12:00 - Is Loki really constrained by fans 
12:01 - 16:16 - What does it take for young directors like Loki to work with superstars
16:17 - 20:40 - How does Loki see the audience's fixation on box-office numbers
20:41 - 24:38 - Who does Loki think is the villain of Leo? 
24:39 - 25:43 - Loki opens about the Hulk Connect in Leo
25:44 - 28:56 - Is Leo a good person or a bad person? 
28:57 - 32.30 - Is Loki glorifying the bad guy in Leo? 
32:31 - 32:56 - What is Parthiban's take on a drug-free society? 
32:57 - 33.24 - Does Loki really think the twin angle worked in favour of the film? 
33:25 - 37:58 - How does Loki work with his writing room? 
37:59 - 42:05 - Does Loki feel the pressure of casting the big names
42:06 - 50:00 - The big question of Loki and LCU

snippet.title: Battle Like Champions' Champion! (Clash of Clans Season Challenges)
snippet.description:
The Champions' Champion skin joins the pantheon of Heroes as we celebrate this year's World Championship, live on Nov 24-26! Get your tickets now at https://supr.cl/clashfest2023! 


Follow us on our Socials!
Twitter â–º https://twitter.com/ClashofClans/
Instagram â–º https://www.instagram.com/clashofclans 
Facebook â–º https://www.facebook.com/ClashofClans 
TikTok â–º https://www.tiktok.com/@clashofclans

Attack. Defend. Strategize. Download for free for mobile devices. http://supr.cl/ThisArmy

From rage-Â­filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/

https://supercell.com/en/privacy-policy/

snippet.title: Easily 3 Star the Champions' Champion Challenge (Clash of Clans)
snippet.description:
3 Star Guide for the Champions Champion Challenge in Clash of Clans! This CoC Event attack showcases the Champions Royal Champion Skin which is available in the November Gold Pass. Supporting the channel with code judo before purchasing is much appreciated! Whilst this challenge is not the most straight forward to beat I was able to consistently get the 3 Stars with this strategy which helps to teach you aspects of the game too. Clash On!

snippet.title: The Beatles - Now And Then (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
Now and Then's eventful journey to fruition took place over five decades and is the product of conversations and collaborations between the four Beatles that go on to this day. The long mythologised John Lennon demo was first worked on in February 1995 by Paul, George and Ringo as part of The Beatles Anthology project but it remained unfinished, partly because of the impossible technological challenges involved in working with the vocal John had recorded on tape in the 1970s. For years it looked like the song could never be completed. But in 2022 there was a stroke of serendipity. A software system developed by Peter Jackson and his team, used throughout the production of the documentary series Get Back, finally opened the way for the uncoupling of Johnâ€™s vocal from his piano part. As a result, the original recording could be brought to life and worked on anew with contributions from all four Beatles. This remarkable story of musical archaeology reflects The Beatlesâ€™ endless creative curiosity and shared fascination with technology. It marks the completion of the last recording that John, Paul and George and Ringo will get to make together and celebrates the legacy of the foremost and most influential band in popular music history.

Video Director: Peter Jackson
Video Producers: Peter Jackson, Clare Olssen, Jonathan Clyde
Audio Producers: Paul McCartney and Giles Martin
Production Company: WingNut Films Productions Ltd

Pre-order Now And Then: https://TheBeatles.lnk.to/NowAndThenYT
Pre-order Red and Blue: https://TheBeatles.lnk.to/RedAndBlue2023YT

snippet.title: Baby planning in Village | Nakkalites Fzone
snippet.description:
#partnership 

Download Duolingo for free - https://app.adjust.net.in/15g5xeol

For  Advertisement Please Contact - business@nakkalites.in

----------------------------------------------

Join the Nakkalites Fzone team as they explore the challenges and joys of baby planning in a rural village. From traditional rituals to modern parenting techniques, this heartwarming video showcases the unique experiences and support systems that exist in rural communities. Get ready for laughter, tears, and a deeper appreciation for the beauty of village life as we follow couples on their journey towards parenthood.

snippet.title: PART 2 Leo Post-release Lokesh Kanagaraj Interview with Sudhir Srinivasan | Leo | Vijay | Trisha
snippet.description:
In this spoiler-filled interaction with Sudhir Srinivasan, #LokeshKanagaraj talks about all things #Leo, bringing #Vijay into the LCU, and more 

This is the SECOND part of the interaction

00:00 - 5:22 - Including History of Violence, what are the other inspirations in Loki's films

05:23 - 07:00 - How did Loki sketch the husband-wife equation in Leo

07:01 - 09:44 - How did the hyena come into the Loki Universe

09:45 - 12:08 - What does Loki think of how people connect the hyena metaphor and other layers of Leo 

12:09 - 14:23 - What elevated Loki's cinematic knowledge

14:24 - 17:48 - What does Loki think of the audience understanding? 

17:49 - 19:37 - What are the plans for the hyena in the LCU? 

19:38 - 20:49 - Will Loki attempt the horror genre? 

20:50 - 23.58 - How does Loki zero in on the retro songs in his films? 

23:59 - 26:16 - How does Loki create an atmosphere for usage of these songs? 

26:17 - 27:20 - What inspired Loki to make that badass Vijay intro card?

27:21 - 28:11 - Why does Loki believe second time is the charm? 

28:12 - 28:38 - Loki on finally bringing Mansoor Ali Khan into the LCU

28:39 - 29:57 - What were the steps Loki took to ensure Parthiban's body adapted to the war scars?
 
29:58 - 32:16 - How important is Anirudh to Loki's films? 

32:17 - 34:27 - What were the various contributions of Anirudh to LEO? 

34:28 - 36:14 - How does Loki work with Anbariv to get the fight choreography on point in Leo? 

36:15 - 37:35 - Does Loki think that the stunts got a bit generic in certain scenes in the second half? 

37:36 - 39:24 - What was the most satisfying response Loki got post the release of Leo? What was his biggest takeaway? 

39:25 - 41:10 - Loki opens up on the LCU Routemap
 
41:11 - 43:23 - Loki signs off by talking about his next biggie,  Thalaivar 171


Follow us on

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/XpressCinema/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/XpressCinema
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/xpresscinema/

For more film news, interviews and reviews, go to: http://www.cinemaexpress.com

Cinema Express is a wing of The New Indian Express, and gives you the latest in the world of cinema, with special emphasis on South India, and particular distaste for gossip. The New Indian Express is published by Express Publications (Madurai) Limited from 25 centres in Tamil Nadu, Karnataka, Andhra Pradesh, Kerala and Odisha.
The company also publishes the Tamil daily, Dinamani, Cinema Express (Tamil), Malayalam Varika (Malayalam), Sakhi (Kannada), and Sunday Standard from New Delhi.

Sundar pays Jetha a surprise visit and assures her that Daya may return by Diwali. Jetha is ecstatic by the news. snippet.title: Emiway x Savlon Swasth India â€“ HAATH DHONA COOL HAI #HandwashLegend ft. The Dharavi Dream Project
snippet.description:
This Iconic Hip-Hop move ğŸ‘ğŸ¼ is now the HANDWASHING Move!
Now after the hack, comes the track!

The track aims to make washing hands with Handwash or Soap cool in the minds of children, keeping them healthy and safe from various illnesses.

Letâ€™s all wash our hands and become a #HandwashLegend.
___

ITC's Savlon Swasth India Mission - one of the largest school programmes of its kind, is committed to seeding hand hygiene habits in over 85 lakh school children, through continuous awareness and engagement activities.  
___

The Dharavi Dream Project After School of Hip-Hop is a non-profit organisation based in Mumbai. Through various educational programmes, mentorships and community engagement initiatives, it supports children living in Dharavi, Mumbai which today is known for its culturally vibrant hip-hop talent.

#HandwashingForAll #SavlonSwasthIndiaMission
___

Episode 3917: Babita Ka Mushkil Gift
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha gets worried about Babita's gift as she wishes to have a present related to the Moon. Jetha falls asleep while engrossed in his thoughts and he dreams about it. In his dream, Jetha and Babita have landed on the Moon through a rocket. Babita is extremely happy and she shows gratitude to Jetha for fulfilling her wish. Jetha's beautiful dream gets jeopardized when Sundar appears and offers him a glass of water. Watch the episode to find out what happens further!

Bhide has come to Jetha's house to complain about Tapu's carelessness in his studies. Jetha challenges Bhide on the same and informs him that Tapu is busy studying. They all find out that Tapu was reading comics all this while and Jetha gets angry at him. Later, Tapu's class teacher tells everyone that they will be having a parent-teacher meeting which is mandatory for all to attend.

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalalâ€™s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch all the fun episodes of TMKOC - Revisit The Journey: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cSkLfD49YxG8YsjmWdKNU0r

snippet.title: Minecraft CHICKEN vs HUNTER
snippet.description:
Minecraft CHICKEN vs HUNTER... I have to take a CHICKEN to beat the ender dragon. My friend has to stop me. Should be easy right?

Follow my socials:
â½ Twitter - @dream
â½ Instagram - @dreamwastaken
â½ Snapchat - @dream

George: @GeorgeNotFound 

This video is a different Minecraft challenge concept that we have never done before! It's similar to Minecraft Manhunt, in that I have to beat the game while George tries to hunt the CHICKEN, instead of me. The chicken heals over time like a player, and has 20 hearts.

It's a race, and it's super intense and we had a lot of laughs. I love doing these challenges.

Not Minecraft, But Water Rises or Minecraft, But Lava Rises, or any other but challenge like that. This is a speed run / speed runner of Minecraft against a killer / assassin

#MinecraftChallenge
